data.title: First Test, day four: over by over

data.text:
A peculiar moment as Billy Bowden, the umpire, consults with Inzamam, presumably asking which bowler he’s going to use next. The Pakistan captain intimates that he wishes to continue with Shabbir Ahmed, so the umpire offers the light to the England batsmen. They take it of course and that’s the close.

England will chase the 174 they still need tomorrow.
